query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow') AND t.name IN ('asp.net-mvc-3',
'bash',
'c++11',
'command-line',
'dataframe',
'date',
'function',
'google-chrome',
'hibernate',
'linux',
'visual-studio')
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000;
